        "bullet_point": {
            "value": [
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "FROZEN 2 CONFETTI HAIR BRUSH: Perfect for any little princess in training, Frozen 2 Anna and Elsa movie fans will learn to love brushing their hair with this printed, square paddle hair brush; With soft and flexible nylon bristles, an ergonomic and easy to grip handle and fun Frozen 2 princess design, Frozen 2 fans will soon have perfect princess hair just like Elsa and her sister Anna",
                    "marketplace_id": "ATVPDKIKX0DER"
                },
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "FLEXIBLE NYLON BRISTLES: Flexible, soft, nylon bristles work through tangles without pulling or tugging; a wide, flat base covers a broad surface area of hair and the cushioned bristle body allows for gentle brushing and styling; Great for all hair types and lengths and will work when brushing hair extensions or ponytail extensions",
                    "marketplace_id": "ATVPDKIKX0DER"
                },
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "TEACHES PERSONAL GROOMING: Gifting your Frozen 2 princess fan their very own hair brush will teach them personal grooming skills and help them develop their fine motor skills too, as they learn to brush and de-tangle their own hair after a shower or bath; plus, kids will love seeing the gold leaf confetti float around the top of the hair brush as they brush their hair!",
                    "marketplace_id": "ATVPDKIKX0DER"
                },
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "HOW TO USE SOFT BRISTLE BRUSH: To de-tangle on wet or dry hair, start by brushing out the ends and work your way up to the crown; if your little one has fun colored hair extensions, hold the hair below the top of the extension and brush away tangles; all of the above will help to avoid unnecessary tugging and pulling that breaks the hair",
                    "marketplace_id": "ATVPDKIKX0DER"
                },
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "SPECIFICATIONS: Brush Dimensions: 3.5 x 2 x 8 inches; Color: Multi; Brush Material: Plastic; Bristle Material: Nylon",
                    "marketplace_id": "ATVPDKIKX0DER"
                }
            ],
